cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.IT. 

The paper deals with a combination of combinatorial optimization and machine learning, specifically in the context of bandit problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves game theory (cs.GT) and information theory (cs.IT) in its analysis of the upper bounds on regret.
